Variaveis

g_legend<-function(a.gplot){
  tmp <- ggplot_gtable(ggplot_build(a.gplot))
  leg <- which(sapply(tmp$grobs, function(x) x$name) == "guide-box")
  legend <- tmp$grobs[[leg]]
  return(legend)}


base %>% 
  select(pk_customer,is_social_login,is_login,is_search,is_size_guide,is_fit_finder,is_filter,is_sort,
         product_view,add_to_cart,remove_from_cart,add_to_favorites,is_view_favorites,
         is_content,is_my_account,is_menu,is_view_sizes,is_faq,qtt_cross_device,
         checkout,is_purchase) %>% 
  melt(id.vars = c("pk_customer", "is_purchase")) %>% 
  group_by(is_purchase,variable) %>% 
  mutate(value = ifelse(value>=1,1,0)) %>% 
  summarise(contagem = sum(value)) %>% 
  filter(is_purchase == 1) %>% 
  inner_join(
    base %>% 
      select(pk_customer,is_social_login,is_login,is_search,is_size_guide,is_fit_finder,is_filter,is_sort,
             visitduration,product_view,add_to_cart,remove_from_cart,add_to_favorites,is_view_favorites,
             is_content,is_my_account,is_menu,is_view_sizes,is_faq,qtt_cross_device,
             checkout,is_purchase) %>% 
      melt(id.vars = c("pk_customer")) %>% 
      group_by(variable) %>% 
      filter(value > 0) %>% 
      summarise(total = n()),
    by = 'variable'
  ) %>% 
  mutate(porcentagem = contagem/total) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_col(aes(y=reorder(variable, porcentagem), x=porcentagem, fill= 'variable'), show.legend = F)+
  geom_vline(xintercept = media_compra, lty = 5, alpha = 0.4)+
  scale_x_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format(), breaks = seq(0,1, by = 0.15))+
   labs(title = "Porcentagem de clientes com compra na primeira visita por comportamento",
       x = "Porcentagem",
       y = "Comportamento"
       )

base %>% 
  mutate(visitduration = round(visitduration/60),
         is_purchase = ifelse(is_purchase ==0, 'Sem Compra', 'Com Compra')) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_boxplot(aes(x=is_purchase, y=visitduration, color=is_purchase), show.legend = F)+ 
  ylim(0,100)+
  #ylim(0,100)+
  theme(title = element_text(size = 10),
        axis.text = element_text(size = 8),
        #legend.position="bottom",
        axis.text.x = element_text(size = 8)
        )+
   labs(title = "Tempo de visita Por Grupo",
       x = "",
       y = "Tempo Visita (minutos)",
       caption = "X-Limitado entre 0-100",
       colour = "Comportamento"
       ) +
  coord_flip()

total <- as.integer(x %>% summarise(n()))

y <- x %>% 
  group_by(is_purchase) %>%  
  summarise(Quantidade_clientes = total,
            Porcentagem_compra =  n()/total) %>% 
  filter(is_purchase == 1)

porcentagem_compra <- as.numeric(y %>% select(Porcentagem_compra))

y %>% 
  mutate(grupo = 'Clientes com Sort') %>% 
  mutate(Porcentagem_compra = paste(round(Porcentagem_compra*100,2),'%', sep="")) %>% 
  select(grupo, Quantidade_clientes, Porcentagem_compra)%>% 
  knitr::kable()%>%   kable_styling(bootstrap_options = "striped", full_width = T, font_size = 12)
grupo Quantidade_clientes Porcentagem_compra
Clientes com Sort 409051 25.65% 
base %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_boxplot(aes(x=is_social_login, y=qtd_compra2, color = qtd_compra2), show.legend = F) +
  #xlim(0, 20)+
  theme(legend.position="bottom",
        axis.text = element_text(size = 8),
        axis.text.x = element_text(size = 8)
        )+
   labs(title = "Quantidade de vezes que cada cliente teve esse comportamento na primeira visita",
        #subtitle = "Considerando só clientes que tiveram esse comportamento pelo menos uma vez",
        x = "",
        y = "Quantidade de Compras"
        #caption = "Log transformation"
       )

plot1 <- x %>% 
      select(pk_customer,is_login,is_search,is_size_guide,is_fit_finder,is_filter,is_sort,
             visitduration,product_view,add_to_cart,remove_from_cart,add_to_favorites,is_view_favorites,
             is_content,is_my_account,is_menu,is_view_sizes,is_faq,qtt_cross_device,
             checkout,is_purchase) %>% 
  melt(id.vars = c("pk_customer", "is_purchase")) %>% 
  filter(value > 0,
         !is.na(value)) %>% 
  group_by(variable,is_purchase) %>% 
  summarise(porcentagem = n()/total) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_col(aes(x=porcentagem, y=reorder(variable,porcentagem), fill = as.factor(is_purchase)))+
  scale_x_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format(), breaks = seq(0,1, by = 0.25))+
  theme(legend.position="bottom",
        axis.text = element_text(size = 8),
        axis.text.x = element_text(size = 8)
        )+
   labs(x = "Quantidade de Clientes",
       y = "Comportamentos",
       fill = "Flag Compra"
       )


plot2 <- x %>% 
      select(pk_customer,is_login,is_search,is_size_guide,is_fit_finder,is_filter,is_sort,
             visitduration,product_view,add_to_cart,remove_from_cart,add_to_favorites,is_view_favorites,
             is_content,is_my_account,is_menu,is_view_sizes,is_faq,qtt_cross_device,
             checkout,is_purchase) %>% 
  melt(id.vars = c("pk_customer", "is_purchase")) %>% 
  filter(value > 0,
         !is.na(value)) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_bar(aes(y=reorder(variable,variable,length), fill = as.factor(is_purchase)), position = 'fill')+
  geom_vline(xintercept = porcentagem_compra, lty = 5, alpha = 0.4)+
  scale_x_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format(), breaks = seq(0,1, by = 0.25))+
   labs(x = "Porcentagem",
       y = "",
       colour = "Comportamento"
       )

mylegend<-g_legend(plot1)

grid.arrange(arrangeGrob(plot1 + theme(legend.position="none"),
                         plot2 + theme(legend.position="none"),
                         top = 'Compras com Social Login junto com outros comportamentos',
                         nrow=1),
             mylegend, nrow=2,heights=c(10, 1))
